"兩難：民情洶湧vs 10萬蚊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d760f56a9367554f1aa5ffc84449ea8e899575","tid":2147631,"uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"黃毓民：黎智英的總辭説法根本係繼續跪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144099</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<strong><em>黎智英説：「香港政府延遲立法會選舉，又DQ民主派參選資格。<span class=\"red\">如果四位遭DQ的民主派候選人唔可以參加嚟緊嘅立法會會議，泛民應該要面對總辭既問題。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民 + 梁錦祥：<br />\n<br />\n呢個係有條件既總辭。根據黎智英講法，並唔係因為佢延期選舉而總辭，亦唔係因為佢DQ 12個民主派參選資格令立法會毫無意義而總辭，<span class=\"red\">而係如果楊岳橋、郭榮鏗 、郭家麒及梁繼昌無得延任，先要「面對總辭」。 咁即係話，如果呢四個入到去續任，唔使DQ多一次繼續做立法會議員，咁你就OK啦唔使總辭？ 呢個係一個要求有得跪低嘅總辭。</span><br />\n<br />\n倒不如話「俾我入去啦，求吓你比我入去啦，入咗去我就唔會搞事架啦」</em></strong>&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b582bb478e8c9583d3fe92c4e50a972a820319d","tid":2147631,"uid":254183,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"520fee626a1753ce8cfb54ab022b338d0d724d1e","tid":2147631,"uid":60527,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"兩難：民情洶湧vs 10萬蚊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"係人都揀10萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc665ba8f96966c6f8b77e1247177b14dea51591","tid":2147631,"uid":43696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"10萬一個月 <br />\n未計請人果20幾萬津貼<br />\n<br />\n叫佢地總辭就亡黨"},{"pid":"b33759d7884fa554b22e469479ccc9aa00533c52","tid":2147631,"uid":55493,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:28:11.000Z","msg":"關鍵野有邊次係靠否決權阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你個關鍵否決權係有用就唔洗搞到宜家噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他野都阻唔到時點解會覺得更大鑊嘅野會靠關鍵否決權擋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警暴都阻唔到，點解覺得政改會靠議會阻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廿年前我仲信，今年唔再信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcc016e0c7d4d80bc631340c0e7dfb835e8b534","tid":2147631,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"關鍵呢兩粒字畀你班民主派玩到爛晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d7b2b5cf9c19c6b4f04532c1fd4d579e9b7f05","tid":2147631,"uid":50275,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751738ab9f84ef3b0000063ed775b3d2bbcf39ec","tid":2147631,"uid":254183,"like":18,"dislike":32,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"意思係好驚冇左份糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"咪篤爆啦"},{"pid":"238273e6ec88b9f7db9f29d5487e6d0d8370f3d6","tid":2147631,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"654cbac408b970cde23a3c71e4e39698087dbc0a","tid":2147631,"uid":271130,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0