"tid":2147631,"uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"黃毓民：黎智英的總辭説法根本係繼續跪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144099</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<strong><em>黎智英説：「香港政府延遲立法會選舉，又DQ民主派參選資格。<span class=\"red\">如果四位遭DQ的民主派候選人唔可以參加嚟緊嘅立法會會議，泛民應該要面對總辭既問題。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民 + 梁錦祥：<br />\n<br />\n呢個係有條件既總辭。根據黎智英講法，並唔係因為佢延期選舉而總辭，亦唔係因為佢DQ 12個民主派參選資格令立法會毫無意義而總辭，<span class=\"red\">而係如果楊岳橋、郭榮鏗 、郭家麒及梁繼昌無得延任，先要「面對總辭」。 咁即係話，如果呢四個入到去續任，唔使DQ多一次繼續做立法會議員，咁你就OK啦唔使總辭？ 呢個係一個要求有得跪低嘅總辭。</span><br />\n<br />\n倒不如話「俾我入去啦，求吓你比我入去啦，入咗去我就唔會搞事架啦」</em></strong>&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"又話收山？"},{"pid":"0aae613d8c2c8f9e9c4d288291578c7ffd2afd16","tid":2147631,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:50:40.000Z","msg":"愈改愈獨裁咪好，加速支港融合，金融中心死期指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37340bbabe033b529ea18b009c49a1be03497df","tid":2147631,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b33759d7884fa554b22e469479ccc9aa00533c52","tid":2147631,"uid":55493,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:28:11.000Z","msg":"關鍵野有邊次係靠否決權阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你個關鍵否決權係有用就唔洗搞到宜家噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他野都阻唔到時點解會覺得更大鑊嘅野會靠關鍵否決權擋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警暴都阻唔到，點解覺得政改會靠議會阻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廿年前我仲信，今年唔再信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"佢所指的關鍵否決權係指偽政改方案要全體2/3（47票）先過到<br />\n2015仲話要幾個泛民轉軚先過到，高登果班仲開埋賠率表賭邊d會轉軚。<br />\n湯家驊直頭係列為1賠1，話佢實轉軚。<br />\n<br />\n【可投注】政 改 投 票 參 考 賠 率<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/5897790/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F5897790%2Fpage%2F1&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=d2ba7b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/5897790/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b92d862273e0dc43a613cdc99ad80eb6acafb3ac","tid":2147631,"uid":51621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"民主派係邊次重要事件用過否決權?"},{"pid":"cd6c9433fed22462c4e59b5a9c0bef33d13ac291","tid":2147631,"uid":286685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b92d862273e0dc43a613cdc99ad80eb6acafb3ac","tid":2147631,"uid":51621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"民主派係邊次重要事件用過否決權?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"2012 DQ甘乃威 (27:0否決)<br />\n2012 DQ梁國雄 (25:19否決)<br />\n2015 偽政改方案 (28:8否決)<br />\n2018 DQ鄭松泰(25:39否決)<br />\n2019 DQ陳淑莊(24:29否決)<br />\n2019 DQ邵家臻(25:31否決)"},{"pid":"dc8789be47080ac7d7be02f712668678bc6f70a8","tid":2147631,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a462e2076a01e53deaddaecb9a6e536732c42338","tid":2147631,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ba1ea2dda530bda3880d3862673184f1e11a877","tid":2147631,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,