:"33f2467e767e790e878c1a9eac021bdfb537a1dd","tid":2147631,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"有幾關鍵?<br />\n睇過?<br />\n否決左國安法未?"},{"pid":"786211c4b0a539658de47a879f710140df1e979a","tid":2147631,"uid":239855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"咁否決左國安法未"},{"pid":"7049dba65f4392db885c9f9756018d2e44492d8c","tid":2147631,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"如果4個被DQ嘅可以入返去<br />\n泛民應該照接受委任<br />\n入咗去之後再總辭<br />\n不過留返4個被DQ嘅喺入面"}],"pinned":{"pid":"02d760f56a9367554f1aa5ffc84449ea8e899575","tid":2147631,"uid":219007,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"黃毓民：黎智英的總辭説法根本係繼續跪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144099</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<strong><em>黎智英説：「香港政府延遲立法會選舉，又DQ民主派參選資格。<span class=\"red\">如果四位遭DQ的民主派候選人唔可以參加嚟緊嘅立法會會議，泛民應該要面對總辭既問題。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民 + 梁錦祥：<br />\n<br />\n呢個係有條件既總辭。根據黎智英講法，並唔係因為佢延期選舉而總辭，亦唔係因為佢DQ 12個民主派參選資格令立法會毫無意義而總辭，<span class=\"red\">而係如果楊岳橋、郭榮鏗 、郭家麒及梁繼昌無得延任，先要「面對總辭」。 咁即係話，如果呢四個入到去續任，唔使DQ多一次繼續做立法會議員，咁你就OK啦唔使總辭？ 呢個係一個要求有得跪低嘅總辭。</span><br />\n<br />\n倒不如話「俾我入去啦，求吓你比我入去啦，入咗去我就唔會搞事架啦」</em></strong>&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}